name: swag tumblr Logo
description:
This is a userstyle that replaces the "tumblr." logo with "swag."
Yes, there is another one of these and I was previously using it, however that swag logo was very choppy and didn't look much like the current tumblr logo. You'll find that this one is a high quality logo.
